dct_title_s: Moscovia que & Alba Russia nõ cõtenta Europeę
dct_description_sm: Bar scale on map given in "Scala miliarium Germanicorũ" (90 units [= 5.1 cm]).
Oriented with north toward left of sheet.
Decorative cartouches, ship, sea monster, flying bat, and other fauna (e.g. horses).
Pictorial vignettes of figures, including encampments and bear-baiting.
Descriptive text throughout, including historical information.
